These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, spinach, apple, kale
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, handball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
2. the person eating spinach is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person eating apple is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is not the person eating apple##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | spinach   | kale    | tomato    | apple |
| Sport      | volleyball | baseball | handball | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, superhero, western, romance
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, lettuce, onion
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
4. the person watching superhero movies is not the person eating grapefruit##6
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
8. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching epic movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | superhero  | western    | epic | romance    |
| Food       | onion | grapefruit | lettuce  | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, sprite, water
City: venice, edinburgh, hannover, prague
1. the person drinking water is not the person traveling to venice##6
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is not the person drinking sprite##6
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
6. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
7. the person traveling to venice is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | water       | hot-chocolate  | fanta  | sprite |
| Job        | hannover | prague | edinburgh | venice  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, malaysian, indian, spanish
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, train, trike
1. the indian is on the left of the spanish##1
2. the malaysian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the trike is not the malaysian##6
4. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the spanish is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | malaysian | indian | spanish     | dutch |
| Transport   | subway     | train    | quad-bike | trike    |

