.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, iced-tea, milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, surfing, lacrosse, soccer
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
3. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5
4. the person drinking fanta is not the person who's sport is soccer##6
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is not the person drinking 7up##6
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | 7up        | milk | iced-tea | fanta |
| Transport   | soccer | water-polo | surfing     | lacrosse   |

