2. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
3. the social-worker is on the right of the journalist##1
4. the journalist is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
5. the japanese is on the left or right of the journalist##3
6. the coach is on the left or right of the thai##3
7. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the japanese##5
8. the brazilian is not the social-worker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | brazilian  | thai        | japanese      | canadian          |
| Job        | coach | journalist | social-worker | photographer |

