.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: chestnut, purple, light-blue, white
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, skateboard, subway
1. the person who likes chestnut is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the helicopter is not the person who likes white##6
3. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person who likes light-blue##5
4. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the subway is the person who likes light-blue##1
7. the person who likes chestnut is not the person driving the subway##6
8. the person who likes purple is somewhere to the right of the person who likes white##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | chestnut  | light-blue | white    | purple |
| Transport   | helicopter | subway | skateboard | airplane  |

