.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, pepper, carrot, corn
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, surfing, swimming, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is golf is not the person eating orange##6
2. the person eating corn is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person eating corn is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person eating carrot is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
6. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person eating pepper##6
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
8. the person eating carrot is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | carrot | orange        | corn  | pepper     |
| Sport   | golf     | weightlifting | surfing | swimming |

