.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, baccarat, montecristo, swisher
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, pop
1. the siglo-smoker is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
2. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the siglo-smoker##5
3. the fan indie is not the montecristo-smoker##6
4. the baccarat-smoker is between the fan pop and the montecristo-smoker##2
5. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
6. the fan electronic is between the fan disco and the siglo-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | montecristo | baccarat    | siglo | swisher |
| Music-Genre   | disco         | electronic | pop   | indie     |

