4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is not the person who's sport is cycling##6
6. the person who's sport is basketball is not the person driving the bike##6
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
8. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
