.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-20::.
City: new-york, paris, hannover, miami
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, roller, skateboard, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
2. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is not the person traveling to new-york##6
5. the person traveling to miami is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
6. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | new-york | paris | miami      | hannover   |
| Transport   | snowmobile  | roller   | skateboard | quad-bike |

 